int main() {
    int t;
    cin>> t;
    while(t--) {
        ll n , m;
        cin >> n >> m;
        vector < pair<ll, int > > v(n);
        vector < ll > ans(n);
        ll sum = 0;
        for(int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
            cin >> v[i].first;
            v[i].second = i;
            sum+=v[i].first;
        }
        if( sum > m) {
            cout << -1 << endl;
        } else {
            sort(v.begin(), v.end());
            bool flag = true;
            ll var1 = 0;
            for(int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
                 if(var1 != v[i].first-1){
                    flag = false;
                    break;
                 }
                 ll var2 = m;
                  if(i!=n-1)
                    var2 = v[i+1].first - 1;
                 ll diff = var2 - var1;
                 if(diff < v[i].first || diff%v[i].first!=0)   {
                    flag = false;
                    break;
                }
                var1 = var2;
                ans[v[i].second] = diff / v[i].first;
            }
            if(flag == false){
                cout << -1 << endl;
                continue;
            }
            for(int i = 0; i < n; i++) {
                cout << ans[i] <<" ";
            }
            cout << endl;
        }
    }
	return 0;
}
